headline: Tesla (TSLA) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why

The upgrade was part of a wave of positive developments for the electric vehicle maker. CEO Elon Musk also announced that the company is testing a new Full Self-Driving (FSD) model with significant improvements, which could be released by the end of September.
